  @i1 = i1
  @i2 = i2
  @i3 = i3
  @i4 = i4
  @bias = bias
  loop {
    @out = out(-0.5833951764998154 * @i1, -2.000924155335911 * @i2, -0.33486604163360756 * @i3, -0.4785192804627713 * @i4, -0.24286744503619312 * @bias)

   break unless block_given?
   break unless yield @_outvec
}

end

  @out = 0
end
